Text:
Apparently TPB doesn't like links...

Thank you for your uploads.

I also want to ask if you have the three updates from Lacey circa2010-2011-2012, and ANYTHING from Kristy-lee. You've been a goldmine of AW stuff in the past, here's hoping you've got more.

Thank you for your time!!

I tried to link their model pages but TPB wouldn't let me even if I obfuscated them beyond recognition.

Lacey is a BIG redhead, some of who's sets I've uploaded, and Kristy_lee is a cute blonde that was one of the four in a set known as picnic girls.
Froggie got a green skull.  Congrats!
